title: City Pensions Will Be On the Ballot This Fall 
url: http://www.bizjournals.com/cincinnati/news/2013/08/12/voters-will-have-their-say-on.html
---

Hamilton County Board of Elections has ruled that voters will have an official stake in choosing to make changes to the city&rsquo;s ailing pension system this November. The amendment to Cincinnati&rsquo;s charter would put any new workers hired after the end of the year into a new retirement plan, with the city contributing up to 9 percent of their annual salary.
